issue.title: improve taxonomic overview
issue.body:
an option for downloading full resolution taxonomic overview .png can be a real nice feature. Especially as this can be used in like data papers. In the added image, not all taxonomic groups are visible.

![image](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/3965195/17397375/09e4f34e-5a38-11e6-997c-5ec01845cfdd.png)

It covers all datasets from Belgian publishers!

thanks !
